======================================================================
ADDITIVE STRUCTURE: QR vs INTERVAL k-SUM SOLUTIONS
======================================================================

--- Section 1: M_k - N_k for all primes and odd k ---
  M_k = #{k-tuples from QR summing to 0 mod p}
  N_k = #{k-tuples from {1,...,m} summing to 0 mod p}
  Delta_k = p*(M_k - N_k)

